notifications.payin: TUSDTRX and USDTRX are different currencies! Ensure you understand which coin you wish to exchange before creating a transaction. USDTRX sent to a TUSDTRX address and vice versa cannot be accepted.
HT payments via ERC-20 only. HT payments are accepted via ERC-20 blockchain only. The Huobi chain is not supported on Changelly.
Send REPv2 only. Use contract address 0x221657776846890989a759ba2973e427dff5c9bb. REPv1 is not supported by Changelly anymore.

notifications.payout: Don't forget to include the XRP Destination Tag from your wallet. If it's required but is missing, your Ripples won't be delivered.

notifications.payin: TRX contract payments are not accepted. Send as an ordinary transfer only.
Send new GALA only. Use contract address 0xd1d2Eb1B1e90B638588728b4130137D262C87cae. Old GALA is not supported.
KMD exchanges may take about 2 hours due to many required confirmations.
CELO contract payments not accepted. Send as an ordinary transfer only! CELO exchanges may take up to 2 hours due to many required confirmations.
FIL contract payments not accepted. Send as an ordinary transfer only!
ETH on Ethereum network only. ETH sent via other networks cannot be processed or recovered.
ARRR deposits on Changelly do not require a Memo. Leave the 'Memo' field blank since any irrelevant data in this field will make your deposit invisible to us.
BSV exchanges may take up to 6 hours due to many required confirmations.
BTG exchanges may take 7-8 hours due to many required confirmations.
Exchange FLOKI on BSC only. Use this option exclusively for exchanging FLOKI on the BSC (BEP-20) network. FLOKI sent via other networks cannot be processed or recovered.
Use native USDC Arbitrum only. We accept only Native USDC Arbitrum token, not Bridged USDC Arbitrum. Sending Bridged USDCARB to our USDCARB address may result in the loss of your funds!
FTM payments are accepted only via the Ethereum (ERC-20) network. FTM sent via other networks cannot be processed or recovered. For the FTM MainNet version, select FTMMAINNET.
We only support USDCMATIC with contract address 0x3c499c542cef5e3811e1192ce70d8cc03d5c3359. Alternative contracts cannot be accepted.

notifications.payout: Your wallet's XMR balance may take longer to update after the exchange due to the nature of the XMR network.

notifications.payin: BCHN chain only. Changelly accepts only BCHN chain transfers. BCHA payments will not be processed.
ZEC exchanges may take over 1 hour due to many required confirmations.
We support XVS with contract address 0xcf6bb5389c92bdda8a3747ddb454cb7a64626c63 only. Alternative contracts cannot be accepted.
We support VANRY on the ETH blockchain only. Please send VANRY through the ERC-20 network.
TFUEL contract payments not accepted. Send as an ordinary transfer only!
Send new AXS only. Use contract address 0xbb0e17ef65f82ab018d8edd776e8dd940327b28b. Old AXS is not supported.

notifications.payout: Use whole numbers for NEO. NEO is indivisible and should be in whole numbers. It rounds down if the price rises. Add extra to minimize sudden price drop risks.

notifications.payin: Send MainNet ONT only. Old ONT (NEO token) and ONG are not supported and cannot be recovered.
No re-used IOTA deposit addresses. Always verify you're depositing to a newly generated address. Tokens deposited to previously used addresses cannot be credited.
